# Vite env (only `VITE_*` is exposed to the client).
#
# Local dev with `vite.config.ts` proxy: use same-origin prefix so the browser does not
# hit cross-origin CORS. Requests go to `/api/...` and Vite forwards to FastAPI :8000.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api
#
# Production / `docker build` (no Vite proxy): set full origin, e.g.
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
